            "title": "《異動股》比亞迪挫半成,日前公布9月汽車銷量按年下跌股價照升",
            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p class=\"\">　　《經濟通通訊社3日專訊》比亞迪(<a data-ga-click-item=\"HKS:01211:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/hkstock/quote/01211\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">01211-HK</a>)現價跌5.2%,報108元,該股成交約1254萬股,涉資13.74億元,最高見113元,最低見107.8元。</p></section><p></p><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p class=\"\">　</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p class=\"\">　　比亞迪日前公布,9月汽車銷量39.63萬輛,按年跌5.5%,主因插電式混合動力乘用車銷量18.8萬輛,按年跌25.6%。此外,該集團指,9月汽車產量40.6萬輛,跌8%。不過,數據公布後,該股昨日(2日)反收升逾3%。</p></section><section><p class=\"\">　</p></section><!--$--><!--/$--><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p class=\"\">　　車股今日普遍下跌,尤以新能源車跌幅更顯著,理想汽車(<a data-ga-click-item=\"HKS:02015:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/hkstock/quote/02015\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">02015-HK</a>)跌4.3%,報97.65元;小鵬汽車(<a data-ga-click-item=\"HKS:09868:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/hkstock/quote/09868\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">09868-HK</a>)跌5.2%,報90.1元;蔚來(<a data-ga-click-item=\"HKS:09866:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/hkstock/quote/09866\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">09866-HK</a>)跌2.3%,報59.8元;零跑汽車(<a data-ga-click-item=\"HKS:09863:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/hkstock/quote/09863\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">09863-HK</a>)跌4.1%,報66.15元。而吉利汽車(<a data-ga-click-item=\"HKS:00175:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/hkstock/quote/00175\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">00175-HK</a>)跌2.2%,報19.3元;長汽(<a data-ga-click-item=\"HKS:02333:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/hkstock/quote/02333\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">02333-HK</a>)跌1.2%,報16.8元;廣汽集團(<a data-ga-click-item=\"HKS:02238:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/hkstock/quote/02238\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">02238-HK</a>)跌0.9%,報3.35元。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p class=\"\">　</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p class=\"\">　　現時,恒生指數報27075,跌211點或跌0.8%,主板成交近588億元。國企指數報9627,跌96點或跌1%。恒生科技指數報6575,跌107點或跌1.6%。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p class=\"\">　</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p class=\"\">　　　　　　　　　表列同板塊或相關股份表現</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p class=\"\">　　　　　　　　　============</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p class=\"\">　</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><table><tr><td>股份(編號)</td><td>現價(元)</td><td>變幅(%)</td></tr><tr><td>比亞迪(<a data-ga-click-item=\"HKS:01211:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/hkstock/quote/01211\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">01211-HK</a>)</td><td>108元</td><td>跌5.18%</td></tr><tr><td>理想汽車(<a data-ga-click-item=\"HKS:02015:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/hkstock/quote/02015\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">02015-HK</a>)</td><td>97.65元</td><td>跌4.26%</td></tr><tr><td>小鵬汽車(<a data-ga-click-item=\"HKS:09868:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/hkstock/quote/09868\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">09868-HK</a>)</td><td>90.1元</td><td>跌5.21%</td></tr><tr><td>蔚來(<a data-ga-click-item=\"HKS:09866:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/hkstock/quote/09866\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">09866-HK</a>)</td><td>59.8元</td><td>跌2.29%</td></tr><tr><td>零跑汽車(<a data-ga-click-item=\"HKS:09863:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/hkstock/quote/09863\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">09863-HK</a>)</td><td>66.15元</td><td>跌4.13%</td></tr><tr><td>吉利汽車(<a data-ga-click-item=\"HKS:00175:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/hkstock/quote/00175\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">00175-HK</a>)</td><td>19.3元</td><td>跌2.23%</td></tr><tr><td>長汽(<a data-ga-click-item=\"HKS:02333:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/hkstock/quote/02333\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">02333-HK</a>)</td><td>16.8元</td><td>跌1.18%</td></tr><tr><td>廣汽集團(<a data-ga-click-item=\"HKS:02238:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/hkstock/quote/02238\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">02238-HK</a>)</td><td>3.35元</td><td>跌0.89%</td></tr></table></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p class=\"\">　　(vs)</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p class=\"\"></p></section></main>